Workout: Functional Ausdauer Circuit (≈45 min | Fokus: Ausdauer, Functional)

Warm-Up | 8 min | Dynamic Mobility & Cardio
- Jumping Jacks
    - 60 s | –
- High Knees
    - 30 s | –
- Butt Kicks
    - 30 s | –
- World’s Greatest Stretch
    - 60 s | –
- Inchworm Walkout
    - 6 reps | –
- Shoulder Pass-Through
    - 15 reps | –

Main | 30 min | 3 Runden Circuit
- Sled Push Heavy
    - 20 m / P: 120 s | –
    - 20 m / P: 120 s | –
    - 20 m / P: 120 s | –
- Wall Ball Shot
    - 15 reps / P: 60 s | –
    - 15 reps / P: 60 s | –
    - 15 reps / P: 60 s | –
- Farmer’s Carry (Dumbbell)
    - 40 m / P: 60 s | –
    - 40 m / P: 60 s | –
    - 40 m / P: 60 s | –
- Burpee Broad Jump
    - 10 reps / P: 60 s | –
    - 10 reps / P: 60 s | –
    - 10 reps / P: 60 s | –
- Row Sprint 250 m
    - 250 m / P: 90 s | –
    - 250 m / P: 90 s | –
    - 250 m / P: 90 s | –
- Broad Jump
    - 10 reps / P: 60 s | –
    - 10 reps / P: 60 s | –
    - 10 reps / P: 60 s | –

Cool-Down | 7 min | Mobility & Stretching
- Hip Flexor Stretch (Kneeling)
    - 60 s | –
- Pigeon Pose (Forward)
    - 45 s | –
- Supine Twist
    - 60 s | –
- Child’s Pose
    - 60 s | –
